title: Hugh Jackman named global ambassador for Qantas
text:
Hugh Jackman named global ambassador for Qantas Last updated 12:53, September 8 2015 Twitter 
Award-winning Australian actor Hugh Jackman is Qantas' new official global ambassador. 
Award-winning Australian actor Hugh Jackman is Qantas' new official global ambassador. The X-Men and Les Miserables star, who recently announced a live concert tour of his home country, will promote the airline on the international stage and work with Qantas on projects in Australia. Jackman says he is looking forward to working with the airline to promote Australia as a tourist destination.
